issue.title: Improve handling of symbolic dimensions in the onnxruntime_test.py

repository.name: onnxruntime
repository.description: ONNX Runtime: cross-platform, high performance ML inferencing and training accelerator

issue.body:
**Description**: 

Improve handling of symbolic dimensions in the onnxruntime_test.py script.
If a symbolic dimension is found allow the user to provide a value, or default to 1.

e.g. usage
`python .\onnxruntime_test.py --symbolic_dims batch=1,seqlen=4 onnxruntime\test\testdata\transform\fusion\fast_gelu_use_graph_input.onnx`


**Motivation and Context**
Fix #3940
